data.description: Unique ranch home with a huge lot in the heart of Rockwood.  Don't let the vinyl siding exterior fool you....  this home is like being up north!  Interior is completely knotty pine walls and ceilings plus hardwood floors.  The lot is extra large at 3/4 acres and includes several raised planters in the garden area.  The basement offers a large recreation area with a pool table (included), storage and laundry.  A breezeway with additional storage connects the house to a 2 car garage.  1 Year Home Warranty included.
